{"word":"H4832 - מַרְפֵּא - marpêʼ - mar-pay' - Cure","slug":"H4832","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַרְפֵּא</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>marpêʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mar-pay'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cure"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E8;&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05D0; - marpe&#x0302;'</b> - <i>mar-pay'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H7495\">H7495</a>; properly <i>curative</i>, that is, literally (concretely) a <i>medicine</i>, or (abstractly) a <i>cure</i>; figuratively (concretely) <i>deliverance</i>, or (abstractly) <i>placidity: - </i>([in-]) cure (-able), healing (-lth), remedy, sound, wholesome, yielding."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3416\">H3416</a>, <a href=\"#/H7495\">H7495</a>, <a href=\"#/H7498\">H7498</a>, <a href=\"#/H7499\">H7499</a>, <a href=\"#/H7500\">H7500</a>, <a href=\"#/H7501\">H7501</a>, <a href=\"#/H7505\">H7505</a>, <a href=\"#/H7509\">H7509</a>"}]}